orth in the whole lot, for the whole transaction is a conspiracy. He has treated me very badly, either through malice or ignorance. When I come back to Florence I intend to obtain satisfaction, come what may. No more. I expect to remain here for another month.\r","standoffProperties":[{"id":"4577afcf-b2eb-4258-9172-056bfe6c241d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":5,"value":"f88d4d64-f9b8-4deb-9f5e-597602cbd9b2","text":"Sandr","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"a4ac2aea-4c0a-4069-ae73-01df88ee252c","type":"codex/document-reference","start":7,"end":7,"value":"a029b833-85a4-4f26-974f-696713976440","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"f06e6e8c-feeb-4a6c-82ac-3a9c38b18bec","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":28,"end":29,"value":"f88d4d64-f9b8-4deb-9f5e-597602cbd9b2","text":"h","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"b0a3b038-2de6-4c85-8b6e-41dc941e3ccf","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":118,"end":120,"value":"f88d4d64-f9b8-4deb-9f5e-597602cbd9b2","text":"hi","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"edb33d6e-50bb-47f5-bc8a-85c02bd5b9b5","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":155,"end":155,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"48ccbe9c-9beb-434b-87ff-97cde0c57df1","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":184,"end":189,"value":"756d8bae-0165-47e5-bc9f-e78146c211a2","text":"ducat","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"ab05d44d-a9f6-4a7f-a371-8cfc7f982888","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":194,"end":196,"value":"f88d4d64-f9b8-4deb-9f5e-597602cbd9b2","text":"hi","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"999f9b32-42a1-4489-9c57-34c653a58b6a","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":199,"end":200,"value":"f88d4d64-f9b8-4deb-9f5e-597602cbd9b2","text":"h","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"bfb70ac4-14db-430e-a789-cb07d56cf33c","type":"codex/entity-reference","star